  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7, boil a full kettle, then take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Cut your<strong> carrot[s] </strong>and <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into chips, then add them to a baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray in the oven for 25-30 min or until golden and crispy – these are your <strong>root veg fries</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1605701145303-x200.jpg",
