    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add <strong>half</strong> of your <strong>chicken stock mix </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) to a bowl with 75ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[115ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>and a knob of <strong>butter</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>dried sage</strong> and <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>sage</strong> <strong>stuffing mix</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>stuffing mix </strong>to one side of a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined tray and push it out until approx. the thickness of a pound coin</p><p>Add the<strong> green bean parcel[s]</strong> to the other side of the tray (cooking for 3 or more? Use 2 trays!)</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1605701185407-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
