          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1605701201156-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the chicken is cooking, dissolve your<strong> remaining chicken stock mix </strong>and <strong>Henderson's Relish</strong> in 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[195ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Once the chicken is browned, add 2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tsp] </span><strong>flour</strong> and mix well until it's coated the chicken</p><p>Reduce the heat to low and add the <strong>chicken stock</strong></p><p>Cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the sauce has started to thicken</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1605701212087-x200.jpg",
